OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784229523
OL,3,CDartmoor ponies will be protected at
OL,4,Ccurrent levels, Government says
OL,6,FBut the Environment Department (Defra)
OL,7,Fhas now said the ponies will be
OL,8,Fremoved from stocking rate
OL,9,Fcalculations ` meaning farmers will
OL,10,Fnot face a choice between keeping
OL,11,Fponies and maintaining sheep or cattle.
OL,13,FPony numbers will be monitored across
OL,14,Fthe moor to make sure they remain
OL,15,Fstable.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
