FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784229523
OL,3,CDartmoor ponies will be protected at
OL,4,Ccurrent levels, Government says
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a pony supplement will be
OL,7,Fintroduced into farming schemes to
OL,8,Fremove any financial incentive to
OL,9,Freduce populations, Defra said.
OL,11,FMarian Spain, Natural England chief
OL,12,Fexecutive, said: "Natural England has
OL,13,Falways been clear that Dartmoor's
OL,14,Fponies play a central role in shaping
OL,15,Fthe landscape and supporting nature,
OL,16,Fand we want to see them continue to do
OL,17,Fso.
OL,26,@tD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
