CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784229523
OL,3,CDartmoor ponies will be protected at
OL,4,Ccurrent levels, Government says
OL,6,F"The Government policy changes
OL,7,Fannounced today will enable us to work
OL,8,Fwith farmers to secure the agreements
OL,9,Fwe need to recover nature on Dartmoor.
OL,11,F"We will continue to work with
OL,12,FDartmoor Land Use Managers Group and
OL,13,Fother local groups on the new
OL,14,Fframework to ensure a healthy,
OL,15,Fsustainable future for Dartmoor."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
