PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1784229523
OL,3,CDartmoor ponies will be protected at
OL,4,Ccurrent levels, Government says
OL,6,FPhil Stocker, chairman of the Dartmoor
OL,7,FLand Use Management Group, said: "This
OL,8,Fannouncement gives pony keepers the
OL,9,Freassurance they need that Dartmoor's
OL,10,Fnative pony populations are a valued
OL,11,Fand essential part of the ecology and
OL,12,Fculture of Dartmoor.
OL,14,F"It aligns fully with the DLUMG's
OL,15,Fwork, where we are running trials to
OL,16,Fbuild the evidence that well-managed
OL,17,Fponies, cattle and sheep can improve
OL,18,Fhabitat condition and benefit nature
OL,19,Fmore widely."
OL,26,@oD@bOUvD@AOU{D@MO]
